+---
+
+## 2026-01-20 15:20 - DATA-003
+Session Info: Model $MODEL running on OpenCode
+- Implemented Transfermarkt import script with download, fuzzy player matching, and DB insertion for market values + injuries
+- Added player_injuries_historical table and documented schema
+- Files changed: scripts/import_transfermarkt_dataset.py, src/database/schema.sql, docs/database-schema.md, requirements.txt, ralph/prd.json
+- **Learnings for future iterations:**
+  - Transfermarkt raw CSVs live under datalake/transfermarkt/raw and are fetched from the GitHub repo in scripts/import_transfermarkt_dataset.py
+  - FBref player IDs can be derived from cached player_stats.json using the same stable int logic as the scraper
+  - pytest still fails in tests/test_time_travel_guards.py due to TimeTravelViolationError mismatch (pre-existing)
+---
